{"tid":1905601,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【入貨時機】美股經歷12年以來跌幅最慘烈！世衛：冷靜下來、沒必要恐慌","createTime":"2020-03-01T11:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T11:19:53.000Z","uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ba6bc1dc5532210c2fd700a186240504b2d239f5","tid":1905601,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:06:44.000Z","msg":"2020-03-01 17:41<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XNvNQpA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXNvNQpA.png&h=77110e5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織（WHO）秘書長譚德塞1日表示，全球市場應冷靜下來，努力看到現實，對快速傳播的新型冠狀病毒感到恐慌是不必要的。「我們需要繼續保持理性，不理性帶來不了任何幫助。我們要處理好事實。」<br />\n<br />\n他在利雅德參加一場國際人道主義論壇上接受美國CNBC訪問時說：「我們需要深入研究數據與事實，做正確的事而非恐慌。恐慌與恐懼是最糟糕的。」<br />\n<br />\n美國股市正在經歷2008年金融危機以來跌幅最慘烈的一個星期，道瓊工業平均指數在5天內暴跌3500點，一周跌幅逾13%。"},{"pid":"a2fea8601010cc755f3eae2881a1a0bdaab1c064","tid":1905601,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:09:57.000Z","msg":"你講一講又可以跌多2000點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a434b89e1fbdb152d2d55ec112990cf08c51ed","tid":1905601,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a2fea8601010cc755f3eae2881a1a0bdaab1c064","tid":1905601,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:09:57.000Z","msg":"你講一講又可以跌多2000點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:10:43.000Z","msg":"未必，聯儲局宣佈左可能減息，有可能機會穩到個市"},{"pid":"81c48d063b0fd87dcb1f5c6c520eb016c56fc6dc","tid":1905601,"uid":36455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:13:57.000Z","msg":"要睇美國本土爆唔爆case<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508bdcddf40c478b0d0a9c1f735899a59d2fff5f","tid":1905601,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:19:53.000Z","msg":"買軍事概念股<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" clas